    <item>
      <title>卢拉助手警告支出大笔以提高批准将使他花费2026年选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/brazil-president-lula-s-aides-warn-spending-big-will-cost-2026-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通货膨胀率很高，他在创纪录的低谷中受到了欢迎，一些内部总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达·席尔瓦（Luiz Inacio Lula Da Silva）的政府开始发出可怕的警告：他需要获得巴西的财政房屋，以便在2026年挽救任何重任的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/brazil-president-lula-s-aides-warn-spending-big-will-cost-2026-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊总理说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/joint-eu-borrowing-talks-to-pick-up-steam-greek-premier-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理吉里亚科斯·西塔基斯（Kyriakos Mitsakis）周四表示，欧盟应该“从国防支出中”“从言论到行动”，共同融资正成为如何捍卫该集团利益的对话的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/joint-eu-borrowing-talks-to-pick-up-steam-greek-premier-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Feb 2025 09:55:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
